      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"7. MISSION BEACH ran below expectations last time at Listed level at Turf Paradise (Dirt) over 1207m, finishing fifth and beaten 2.75 lengths. Manuel Americano who has scored on him three times retains the mount. Should be hard to stop. 2. SAWASDEE lines up on the back of a 2.5 lengths fourth over 1207m at Turf Paradise. Race sets up well for him. 3. CODE DUELLO has been racing well and is close to a win, the latest effort a solid second at Santa Anita (Dirt) over 1207m. Can measure up again. 4. ZOFFARELLI stuck on well last start to finish second over 1609m at this track (Turf) after showing good early speed. Must raise the bar but a win is not out of the question.\",\"runners\":[7,2,3,4],\"exclusive\":false}",
